1
00:01:30,940 --> 00:01:35,000
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,350 --> 00:01:35,920
Come on.

3
00:01:35,780 --> 00:01:39,430
[1998]

4
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,300
In a moment,

5
00:01:37,590 --> 00:01:38,400
let's see who

6
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:39,590
can climb up to that pavilion first,

7
00:01:39,590 --> 00:01:40,070
okay?

8
00:01:40,479 --> 00:01:41,070
Ready...

9
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:41,690
Ready...

10
00:01:42,039 --> 00:01:43,000
Go!

11
00:01:44,150 --> 00:01:44,920
Slow down.

12
00:01:45,530 --> 00:01:46,280
Slow down. Be careful.

13
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:47,539
Slow down. Be careful.

14
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:49,229
I'm first! I'm first!

15
00:01:49,229 --> 00:01:50,400
Yeah, you came in first.

16
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:50,870
I couldn't even catch up to you.

17
00:01:50,870 --> 00:01:52,000
I'm losing

18
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:55,759
more than just the memories
of two versions of myself.

19
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:56,820
I'm losing my life,

20
00:01:57,150 --> 00:01:58,150
my feelings,

21
00:01:59,310 --> 00:02:00,350
and the moments

22
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,840
that made me who I am.

23
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,000
Only with those

24
00:02:04,510 --> 00:02:06,560
did I truly exist as myself.

25
00:02:07,070 --> 00:02:07,840
Now,

26
00:02:08,030 --> 00:02:09,630
I can feel something

27
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:11,290
slipping away from me.

28
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,520
And I...

29
00:02:13,430 --> 00:02:14,710
Am fading away.

30
00:02:18,670 --> 00:02:21,460
[Episode 22]
[As I Fade Away]

31
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:26,430
You're back.

32
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,890
Are you alright?

33
00:02:28,910 --> 00:02:29,910
You know already?

34
00:02:30,430 --> 00:02:31,560
How is Zhou Cheng?

35
00:02:32,150 --> 00:02:33,190
He has some minor injuries

36
00:02:33,190 --> 00:02:35,560
and needs to stay in the hospital
for a few days.

37
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:37,190
You haven't eaten yet, have you?

38
00:02:37,190 --> 00:02:38,850
I'll heat up some food for you.

39
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,430
Silly kid.

40
00:02:47,190 --> 00:02:49,280
Don't shoulder everything alone.

41
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:51,310
Laugh if you want to laugh,

42
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:52,710
and cry if you want to cry.

43
00:02:52,870 --> 00:02:54,470
No one will laugh at you.

44
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:35,680
If I hadn't insisted on

45
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,590
digging into it,

46
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:37,520
maybe they wouldn't have...

47
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,180
Zhou Cheng.

48
00:03:39,030 --> 00:03:40,160
It's not your fault.

49
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,030
Zhou Cheng.

50
00:03:43,750 --> 00:03:45,410
I believe it's not your fault.

51
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:49,640
But I don't have that kind of confidence
in myself.

52
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:44,560
Hello.

53
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:45,750
Yes.

54
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:47,870
We worked on the Haihua Hotel project.

55
00:04:47,870 --> 00:04:49,800
Okay, let me take down your number.

56
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:52,600
Okay.

57
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:54,720
Ms. Xia,

58
00:04:55,310 --> 00:04:56,510
3 companies have already approached us

59
00:04:56,510 --> 00:04:57,600
for collaboration.

60
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,630
Then take down

61
00:04:58,630 --> 00:04:59,270
their numbers and info,

62
00:04:59,270 --> 00:05:00,120
and we'll schedule meetings
with them later.

63
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:00,950
I'm going out for a bit now.

64
00:05:00,950 --> 00:05:02,000
We'll set a time tonight.

65
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:02,390
Okay.

66
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:08,410
Has Xiaolan always been like this?

67
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,750
You mean busy?

68
00:05:10,510 --> 00:05:12,040
Ever since I met Ms. Xia,

69
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:13,520
she's never stopped

70
00:05:13,630 --> 00:05:14,760
for a single moment.

71
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:18,040
If you hadn't told me,

72
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,360
I wouldn't have been able to tell

73
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,920
from her face at all

74
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:24,380
that her boyfriend just had an accident.

75
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:26,220
That's just how Ms. Xia is.

76
00:05:26,270 --> 00:05:27,430
She never lets her personal emotions

77
00:05:27,430 --> 00:05:28,430
affect her work.

78
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,510
Last time she got injured,

79
00:05:30,510 --> 00:05:32,170
it didn't slow her down at all.

80
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,340
Brittle sticks break easily.

81
00:05:36,830 --> 00:05:37,240
Look, you two

82
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,240
grew up together.

83
00:05:38,390 --> 00:05:39,270
Why didn't you

84
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:40,120
protect her properly?

85
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:40,750
Auntie, Auntie.

86
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:41,750
Please calm down.

87
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:42,950
Zhou Cheng really did

88
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:44,140
want to pull Jiang Yan out at that moment,

89
00:05:44,140 --> 00:05:45,400
but before he could...

90
00:05:49,630 --> 00:05:50,159
Auntie.

91
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:51,390
Uncle.

92
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:53,360
Regarding what happened to Jiang Yan...

93
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:53,920
Regarding what happened to Jiang Yan,

94
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,920
you must take full responsibility.

95
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:58,920
Sure.

96
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:00,430
I'll take responsibility too.

97
00:06:00,430 --> 00:06:01,120
I also grew up

98
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:01,980
with Jiang Yan.

99
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,680
I'll definitely take good care of her.

100
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,120
Wei.

101
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:05,060
Why are you interrupting?

102
00:06:05,060 --> 00:06:06,710
Is this any of your business?

103
00:06:06,870 --> 00:06:07,950
How is it not my business?

104
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:09,000
Of course it is.

105
00:06:09,070 --> 00:06:09,600
Auntie, I think

106
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:10,510
what you said is absolutely right.

107
00:06:10,510 --> 00:06:12,240
Jiang Yan works in Shengcheng,

108
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,480
and we grew up together.

109
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,000
It's only right that Cheng and I

110
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,200
take good care of her.

111
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:18,870
Who are you?

112
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:21,820
Hello, Auntie.

113
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,900
I'm Zhou Cheng's girlfriend.

114
00:06:34,159 --> 00:06:34,620
Xiao...

115
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:44,600
Here.

116
00:06:50,950 --> 00:06:51,480
Xiaolan.

117
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:53,950
That was

118
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,610
Jiang Yan's mother.

119
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,530
Her daughter is badly injured,

120
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,860
so it's understandable she's upset.

121
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,380
How's Jiang Yan doing?

122
00:07:03,070 --> 00:07:05,190
The doctor said she's ready for surgery,

123
00:07:05,190 --> 00:07:07,790
but they don't seem to
have made a decision yet.

124
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:08,490
Xiaolan...

125
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:09,360
Eat first.

126
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:10,920
The food is getting cold.

127
00:07:26,190 --> 00:07:26,630
Hello?

128
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,720
Du Zhaohui, what do you want now?

129
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:39,800
I'm very busy.

130
00:07:39,950 --> 00:07:42,000
If you're going to talk nonsense,
I'll leave right away.

131
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,630
Alright, I'll get straight to the point.

132
00:07:43,630 --> 00:07:45,500
I've got 20 million Hong Kong dollars.

133
00:07:45,500 --> 00:07:46,240
I want to make as much money

134
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,040
as possible in a year.

135
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:47,950
What should I do?

136
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:49,000
Why are you asking me?

137
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:50,159
Because among the people I know,

138
00:07:50,159 --> 00:07:51,560
you're the best at making money.

139
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,600
You're also the least likely

140
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,330
to be bribed,

141
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,560
and the least likely

142
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,610
to be set up as

143
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:56,720
an undercover agent.

144
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:57,390
Du Zhaohui.

145
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:58,800
Even if I knew

146
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,070
how to make more money,

147
00:08:00,270 --> 00:08:01,470
why should I tell you?

148
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,600
I'll pay you.

149
00:08:05,150 --> 00:08:06,420
If I do as you say

150
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,480
and make a profit,

151
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,450
I'll only take back the principal,

152
00:08:08,450 --> 00:08:09,800
and you can take all the profit.

153
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:10,600
I just need to run it through

154
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,330
my accounts.

155
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:16,070
Mr. Du, you're certainly generous.

156
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:20,260
What are you really after?

157
00:08:20,510 --> 00:08:21,560
Twenty million Hong Kong dollars

158
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:23,480
would earn interest
even just sitting in a bank.

159
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,510
Your Du family has so many

160
00:08:24,510 --> 00:08:26,000
passive income businesses.

161
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,530
Why make it so complicated?

162
00:08:30,190 --> 00:08:31,000
Could this have anything to do

163
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:33,000
you fighting for the family assets?

164
00:08:34,909 --> 00:08:35,960
You're truly impressive.

165
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,360
Your analysis was right.

166
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:38,440
Old Man said

167
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:40,909
whoever can make the most money
with 20 million

168
00:08:40,909 --> 00:08:41,360
gets 5%

169
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,000
of the group's shares.

170
00:08:43,789 --> 00:08:44,240
No.

171
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:47,020
You're still not telling the whole truth.

172
00:08:47,020 --> 00:08:48,290
Whoever gets that 5% of

173
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,660
Chengrong Group's shares

174
00:08:49,660 --> 00:08:51,790
will be ahead of
the rest of the Du family.

175
00:08:51,790 --> 00:08:52,550
This isn't just

176
00:08:52,550 --> 00:08:54,210
a battle over 5% of the shares—

177
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:55,840
it's a fight for

178
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,770
the heir of the Du family, isn't it?

179
00:08:57,790 --> 00:08:59,390
Yes, yes, yes. You're right.

180
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,390
But 5%

181
00:09:02,030 --> 00:09:03,630
is not a small amount either.

182
00:09:03,870 --> 00:09:04,670
But of course,

183
00:09:04,810 --> 00:09:05,720
the most important thing is

184
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,120
earning Old Man's favor.

185
00:09:08,150 --> 00:09:09,000
I promise you,

186
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:09,960
if the Du family

187
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,560
ends up under my management,

188
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,120
I'll definitely

189
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,360
shut down

190
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:15,000
all the smuggling businesses.

191
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:15,960
That Jerk Zh...

192
00:09:16,910 --> 00:09:18,320
That boyfriend of yours—

193
00:09:18,630 --> 00:09:19,670
isn't he investigating

194
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:20,800
the smuggling case?

195
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,240
I can give him

196
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,440
all the information.

197
00:09:24,550 --> 00:09:25,750
The Du family's money

198
00:09:25,990 --> 00:09:27,520
is essentially your money.

199
00:09:28,150 --> 00:09:30,530
How could you be willing
to shut down the smuggling business?

200
00:09:30,530 --> 00:09:31,600
Only the money that goes into my pocket

201
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:32,560
is truly mine.

202
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:34,510
That money belongs to the Du family—

203
00:09:34,510 --> 00:09:36,240
and the Du family isn't just me.

204
00:09:36,510 --> 00:09:37,390
I've thought about it.

205
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:38,520
Times have changed.

206
00:09:38,550 --> 00:09:39,210
From now on,

207
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,970
I only want to make clean money.

208
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:42,870
I swear

209
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:45,050
I'll only do legitimate business.

210
00:09:46,670 --> 00:09:48,390
Didn't Chairman Du
propose this competition

211
00:09:48,390 --> 00:09:49,320
just to test

212
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:51,670
you and your younger brother's abilities?

213
00:09:51,670 --> 00:09:53,130
Doesn't asking me for help

214
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:54,260
count as cheating?

215
00:09:54,940 --> 00:09:55,990
Old Man only said

216
00:09:56,020 --> 00:09:57,750
we couldn't use the family's resources.

217
00:09:57,750 --> 00:09:59,360
I don't believe that brat

218
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,810
won't use outside help.

219
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:01,550
Well,

220
00:10:01,790 --> 00:10:03,630
you're not part of the family resources.

221
00:10:03,630 --> 00:10:04,440
What do you say?

222
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,120
I'll give you some time to think about it.

223
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,320
Besides the payment,

224
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:08,440
I've got something else

225
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:09,170
to offer you.

226
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:11,560
What is it?

227
00:10:12,910 --> 00:10:13,720
In a year,

228
00:10:14,270 --> 00:10:15,360
I'll hand Xia Ziyu

229
00:10:15,670 --> 00:10:17,200
over to you. How about that?

230
00:10:18,030 --> 00:10:18,790
Xia Ziyu?

231
00:10:20,150 --> 00:10:21,950
Old Man's new girlfriend, Vivi—

232
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,550
she's also your cousin,

233
00:10:23,550 --> 00:10:24,810
Xia Ziyu.

234
00:10:34,550 --> 00:10:36,510
There's a ship to Gangdao
the day after tomorrow.

235
00:10:36,510 --> 00:10:37,440
If you want to go,

236
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:38,680
get the money ready.

237
00:10:49,070 --> 00:10:51,320
You have no ID and can't speak Cantonese.

238
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:51,670
Go away.

239
00:10:51,670 --> 00:10:52,440
I can wash vegetables and dishes.

240
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:52,960
I can do anything.

241
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:53,910
Go away. Go away.

242
00:10:53,910 --> 00:10:55,110
We're not hiring you.

243
00:10:58,220 --> 00:10:59,070
Look at

244
00:10:59,750 --> 00:11:00,360
that girl.

245
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:04,290
Let's ask her if she's interested.

246
00:11:06,700 --> 00:11:07,510
Hey, beauty.

247
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:10,360
Since you can't speak Cantonese,

248
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:12,020
it's really hard to find a job.

249
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,870
I can introduce a job to you.

250
00:11:17,870 --> 00:11:20,440
Everyone's like this
when they first come here.

251
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:22,840
Let's see how many more days
you can starve.

252
00:11:24,510 --> 00:11:26,170
Why pretend to be so innocent?

253
00:11:26,670 --> 00:11:27,530
Give her a couple of days—

254
00:11:27,530 --> 00:11:28,440
once she thinks it through,

255
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:29,700
she'll come back to us.

256
00:11:38,060 --> 00:11:39,650
Darn northern girl,

257
00:11:39,790 --> 00:11:40,840
cheating me of my money!

258
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:41,500
Pay me back!

259
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:42,790
You scumbag.

260
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:49,000
Tired of living?

261
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:49,630
What if you'd bumped into

262
00:11:49,630 --> 00:11:50,240
our Young Master?

263
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,340
Do you have a death wish?

264
00:11:51,340 --> 00:11:52,200
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

265
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,320
I didn't mean to.

266
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,550
P-Please spare me.

267
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:06,080
Mr. Du, that story

268
00:13:06,270 --> 00:13:08,200
is really full of twists and turns.

269
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:09,120
It's fascinating.

270
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:09,720
Is it?

271
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:11,630
Stories like this happen every day

272
00:13:11,630 --> 00:13:12,870
in Gangdao.

273
00:13:14,270 --> 00:13:16,200
But since she had plastic surgery,

274
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:16,960
how did you know

275
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:17,890
she was Xia Ziyu?

276
00:13:18,470 --> 00:13:20,470
Old Man is suspicious and paranoid.

277
00:13:20,670 --> 00:13:21,910
Of course he'd investigate

278
00:13:21,910 --> 00:13:23,770
everyone by his side thoroughly.

279
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:25,500
So, what do you say?

280
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:26,630
Think it over.

281
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:28,630
If you help me,

282
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:30,840
I'll hand Xia Ziyu over to you.

283
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:32,320
Also,

284
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:33,870
there's no need to worry about Old Man.

285
00:13:33,870 --> 00:13:35,360
He has so many women around him.

286
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,360
Once Vivi's gone,

287
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:38,240
surely some other woman

288
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:39,370
will take her place.

289
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,120
Actually, I'm not interested

290
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:41,780
in Xia Ziyu.

291
00:13:42,630 --> 00:13:43,600
But

292
00:13:43,750 --> 00:13:44,880
I know she caused you

293
00:13:45,070 --> 00:13:46,160
a lot of trouble.

294
00:13:47,060 --> 00:13:48,440
Regarding that trouble,

295
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:49,150
I've already made her

296
00:13:49,150 --> 00:13:50,360
pay double—

297
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,820
she's already a fugitive.

298
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:52,690
Besides,

299
00:13:53,070 --> 00:13:54,480
what use is it to hand Vivi over to me?

300
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:56,750
The one who belongs in prison is Xia Ziyu.

301
00:13:57,480 --> 00:13:59,120
It's just a matter of
changing her identity.

302
00:13:59,120 --> 00:14:00,910
Although it's a bit troublesome,

303
00:14:00,910 --> 00:14:02,240
it's not impossible.

304
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,960
If the reward isn't enough,

305
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,600
feel free to speak up about

306
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:08,000
any other ideas you have.

307
00:14:13,630 --> 00:14:14,890
I've thought about it.

308
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:16,030
It's better

309
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:18,510
not to work with gangsters.

310
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:20,550
Mr. Du, you kidnap people

311
00:14:20,550 --> 00:14:22,200
and throw them into the sea
whenever you feel like it.

312
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:23,390
It really scares me.

313
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:26,080
I'm so sincere about discussing

314
00:14:26,080 --> 00:14:27,600
a multi-million deal with you,

315
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:29,060
yet you call me a gangster?

316
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:31,270
Kidnapping and throwing people
into the sea?

317
00:14:31,270 --> 00:14:32,730
When have I ever done that?

318
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:33,960
After all,

319
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:35,240
I'm easily worth

320
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:36,750
hundreds of millions, okay?

321
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:38,550
I have so much to do every day.

322
00:14:39,480 --> 00:14:41,680
How would I have time for such bad deeds?

323
00:14:41,870 --> 00:14:42,200
Fine.

324
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:43,640
Let me think about it.

325
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,240
But even if I agree,

326
00:14:45,390 --> 00:14:47,320
the consulting fee won't be cheap.

327
00:14:49,560 --> 00:14:51,620
You're not leaving already, are you?

328
00:14:53,390 --> 00:14:53,960
Mr. Du.

329
00:14:54,910 --> 00:14:55,770
Are you willing

330
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:57,420
to sell your house and car?

331
00:14:59,670 --> 00:15:01,120
Vivi is Xia Ziyu?

332
00:15:01,360 --> 00:15:02,480
She had plastic surgery

333
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:03,680
and changed her name.

334
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:05,920
Even though I told Du Zhaohui

335
00:15:06,030 --> 00:15:07,560
I wasn't interested in her,

336
00:15:08,150 --> 00:15:10,150
she's done so many terrible things—

337
00:15:10,150 --> 00:15:10,750
I don't want her

338
00:15:10,750 --> 00:15:12,550
to escape the law's punishment.

339
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:13,750
If she keeps staying in Gangdao

340
00:15:13,750 --> 00:15:14,600
and doesn't come back,

341
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:15,200
is there really

342
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:16,660
nothing we can do about it?

343
00:15:17,560 --> 00:15:18,150
If she keeps staying

344
00:15:18,150 --> 00:15:19,300
in Gangdao,

345
00:15:19,630 --> 00:15:21,270
it's indeed quite troublesome.

346
00:15:21,270 --> 00:15:22,600
To bring her to justice,

347
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:24,360
she must come back first.

348
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,240
And secondly,

349
00:15:25,720 --> 00:15:27,320
we must prove she is Xia Ziyu.

350
00:15:27,830 --> 00:15:29,710
Besides her face and name,

351
00:15:30,590 --> 00:15:32,190
are there other ways

352
00:15:32,470 --> 00:15:34,200
to prove her true identity?

353
00:15:35,300 --> 00:15:36,180
For example,

354
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:37,340
fingerprints,

355
00:15:37,750 --> 00:15:38,360
hair,

356
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:40,110
or blood comparison?

357
00:15:41,750 --> 00:15:42,910
You mean that

358
00:15:43,430 --> 00:15:45,150
DNA identification technology?

359
00:15:45,150 --> 00:15:45,550
Yes.

360
00:15:45,910 --> 00:15:47,040
Is it available now?

361
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:48,550
I heard it is.

362
00:15:48,990 --> 00:15:50,790
I'll ask my contacts
at the Public Security Bureau

363
00:15:50,790 --> 00:15:51,920
to ask around later.

364
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:53,000
Okay.

365
00:15:57,270 --> 00:15:57,840
Xiaolan,

366
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:00,900
stay away from Du Zhaohui.

367
00:16:01,870 --> 00:16:04,030
Jiang Yan has been keeping an eye
on the Du family.

368
00:16:04,030 --> 00:16:06,320
The Du family didn't just get rich
from smuggling.

369
00:16:06,320 --> 00:16:07,080
Even now,

370
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:09,150
they still haven't completely
severed ties.

371
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:09,960
I know Du Zhaohui

372
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:11,720
came to Shengcheng a few years ago.

373
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:12,750
It may seem like

374
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:14,750
he's been doing decent business,

375
00:16:14,750 --> 00:16:15,440
but he can't possibly

376
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:17,240
really cut ties with his family.

377
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:19,150
And even if he's not part of it—

378
00:16:19,150 --> 00:16:19,960
don't forget—

379
00:16:20,790 --> 00:16:21,600
he's not the only son

380
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:22,550
of the Du family.

381
00:16:24,270 --> 00:16:25,320
You mean,

382
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:27,270
if Du Zhaohui

383
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:29,270
gives us information

384
00:16:29,910 --> 00:16:31,750
and the Du family's interests gets harmed,

385
00:16:31,750 --> 00:16:32,670
Du Chengrong

386
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:35,000
won't even spare his own son?

387
00:16:35,510 --> 00:16:36,720
Fathers and sons
turning against each other,

388
00:16:36,720 --> 00:16:37,720
brothers at odds—

389
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:39,380
these are very common.

390
00:16:39,840 --> 00:16:40,750
But if Du Zhaohui

391
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:41,440
really knows

392
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:42,630
information about the smuggling case,

393
00:16:42,630 --> 00:16:43,120
then for you...

394
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:43,650
Xiaolan,

395
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:51,330
you've seen it too.

396
00:16:51,910 --> 00:16:53,640
This matter is very dangerous.

397
00:16:54,150 --> 00:16:54,870
After these two incidents,

398
00:16:54,870 --> 00:16:55,930
I'm even wondering

399
00:16:56,030 --> 00:16:56,620
whether I should

400
00:16:56,620 --> 00:16:58,120
continue investigating this.

401
00:16:58,120 --> 00:16:58,840
I fear

402
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:01,930
I'd bringing danger to others.

403
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:03,790
But can you really

404
00:17:03,790 --> 00:17:05,190
let go of Shi Kai's death?

405
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:08,550
If you can't find the truth,

406
00:17:09,030 --> 00:17:10,760
will you really be able to stop?

407
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:13,339
Then would you still be yourself?

408
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:14,380
Zhou Cheng.

409
00:17:15,069 --> 00:17:16,270
Don't worry about me.

410
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:18,480
I'll protect myself.

411
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:22,550
Mr. Du.

412
00:17:23,550 --> 00:17:24,410
Are you willing

413
00:17:24,589 --> 00:17:26,050
to sell your house and car?

414
00:17:26,869 --> 00:17:28,600
She wants me to tighten my belt?

415
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:30,460
I'd rather be a loan shark.

416
00:17:32,350 --> 00:17:33,510
Is that all you've got?

417
00:17:33,510 --> 00:17:35,710
No wonder Xia Xiaolan doesn't like you.

418
00:17:37,270 --> 00:17:38,730
Young Master, your phone.

419
00:17:42,030 --> 00:17:42,480
Hello?

420
00:17:44,480 --> 00:17:45,240
It's a deal.

421
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:47,650
Don't forget what you promised me.

422
00:17:49,310 --> 00:17:50,440
If I do as you say,

423
00:17:50,750 --> 00:17:51,920
I'll have no way out.

424
00:17:52,790 --> 00:17:53,520
Don't worry.

425
00:17:53,750 --> 00:17:55,010
I'll make sure you win.

426
00:17:56,750 --> 00:17:57,160
Good.

427
00:17:57,790 --> 00:17:59,520
Then I'll make sure you win too.

428
00:18:02,030 --> 00:18:03,430
You'll definitely win,

429
00:18:03,680 --> 00:18:04,480
Young Master.

430
00:18:11,590 --> 00:18:12,540
Many records

431
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:13,830
have become

432
00:18:13,830 --> 00:18:15,270
meaningless numbers.

433
00:18:15,880 --> 00:18:17,270
My memories are fading,

434
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,260
and I'm fading too.

435
00:18:20,350 --> 00:18:21,610
I'm sorry, Zhou Cheng.

436
00:18:22,440 --> 00:18:24,500
I don't know how much time I have left.

437
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:27,110
I just want the smuggling case

438
00:18:27,790 --> 00:18:29,000
and Xia Ziyu's matter

439
00:18:29,750 --> 00:18:30,950
to both come to an end.

440
00:18:34,310 --> 00:18:35,790
Young Master instructed

441
00:18:35,920 --> 00:18:37,440
that no one's allowed in.

442
00:18:38,070 --> 00:18:40,200
I'll let you know if he needs anything.

443
00:18:40,310 --> 00:18:41,110
Young Master.

444
00:18:41,350 --> 00:18:42,200
Where's Old Man?

445
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:44,260
Master went to Nanyang for business.

446
00:18:44,960 --> 00:18:46,220
-You may leave.
-Okay.

447
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:48,720
He went to Nanyang for business?

448
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:57,480
Stepmother, you're so relaxed.

449
00:19:00,240 --> 00:19:02,350
These coffee beans are from South America.

450
00:19:02,350 --> 00:19:03,160
I wonder

451
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:06,010
if they suit your taste, Young Master.

452
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:15,730
Tastes good.

453
00:19:17,130 --> 00:19:18,090
But coffee

454
00:19:18,550 --> 00:19:20,210
is best drunk in a coffee shop.

455
00:19:20,550 --> 00:19:21,880
The beans don't matter.

456
00:19:22,370 --> 00:19:24,100
What matters is the atmosphere

457
00:19:24,510 --> 00:19:25,590
and the company.

458
00:19:28,180 --> 00:19:29,580
I heard a nice coffee shop

459
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:31,520
recently opened in Shengcheng.

460
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:33,280
Vivi, when you have time,

461
00:19:33,480 --> 00:19:35,210
ask Old Man to take you to try it.

462
00:19:38,270 --> 00:19:39,440
Young Master,

463
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:41,970
what do you mean by that?

464
00:19:44,030 --> 00:19:44,960
Nothing really.

465
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:46,310
Just

466
00:19:46,680 --> 00:19:48,410
telling you to go drink coffee.

467
00:19:48,960 --> 00:19:50,070
Don't worry.

468
00:19:50,590 --> 00:19:51,680
With Old Man there,

469
00:19:51,830 --> 00:19:52,960
even in Shengcheng,

470
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:54,730
no one would dare touch you.

471
00:20:00,030 --> 00:20:02,090
Young Master, you're a smart person.

472
00:20:03,110 --> 00:20:04,160
In this family,

473
00:20:04,610 --> 00:20:05,160
you and I are supposed to

474
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:06,440
support each other.

475
00:20:08,030 --> 00:20:09,350
Your relationship with Xia Xiaolan

476
00:20:09,350 --> 00:20:10,610
is none of my business.

477
00:20:10,960 --> 00:20:11,720
But

478
00:20:13,160 --> 00:20:14,830
if you dare ruin my plans,

479
00:20:15,640 --> 00:20:16,830
I'll make you pay.

480
00:20:22,720 --> 00:20:23,480
Since Xia Xiaolan

481
00:20:23,480 --> 00:20:25,000
agreed to work with you,

482
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:26,880
Young Master, I believe you

483
00:20:26,880 --> 00:20:28,160
didn't tell her the full story

484
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:29,240
about us.

485
00:20:30,830 --> 00:20:31,960
A word of advice:

486
00:20:32,470 --> 00:20:34,000
Xia Xiaolan holds grudges.

487
00:20:34,750 --> 00:20:36,070
If you lie to her,

488
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:38,510
she'll make you pay tenfold.

489
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:42,680
Young Master,

490
00:20:43,680 --> 00:20:45,010
watch out for yourself.

491
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,030
We'll

492
00:20:59,030 --> 00:20:59,690
next month.

493
00:21:00,020 --> 00:21:00,880
Will you have enough time

494
00:21:00,880 --> 00:21:01,740
to buy the land?

495
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:04,680
It's not like I can just buy the land

496
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:05,610
whenever I want.

497
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:08,110
Land in Shengcheng is really expensive.

498
00:21:08,110 --> 00:21:09,270
Only those in foreign trade

499
00:21:09,270 --> 00:21:10,720
can afford it right now.

500
00:21:11,110 --> 00:21:12,920
I still need to check the location.

501
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:14,240
I can't afford a big plot,

502
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:15,970
so I'll have to pick carefully.

503
00:21:17,680 --> 00:21:18,790
Anyway, if you need anything,

504
00:21:18,790 --> 00:21:19,720
just let me know.

505
00:21:21,880 --> 00:21:22,400
Look.

506
00:21:22,750 --> 00:21:23,880
According to Gangdao news,

507
00:21:23,880 --> 00:21:24,830
Du Zhaohui is selling

508
00:21:24,830 --> 00:21:26,210
his cars and houses.

509
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:27,440
Is he going bankrupt?

510
00:21:29,880 --> 00:21:30,960
Really?

511
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:32,740
That's great news.

512
00:21:32,880 --> 00:21:34,440
I even want to buy firecrackers

513
00:21:34,440 --> 00:21:35,440
to celebrate.

514
00:21:36,680 --> 00:21:37,590
Why are you reading

515
00:21:37,590 --> 00:21:38,920
Gangdao's newspapers?

516
00:21:39,110 --> 00:21:40,310
Well, Sis Bai said

517
00:21:40,490 --> 00:21:41,720
since we're close to Gangdao,

518
00:21:41,720 --> 00:21:42,350
we might do business there

519
00:21:42,350 --> 00:21:43,790
in the future.

520
00:21:44,240 --> 00:21:45,350
We should read more, learn more,

521
00:21:45,350 --> 00:21:47,150
and get more information first.

522
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:48,750
Sis Bai is right.

523
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:50,790
She thinks even more thoroughly
than I do now.

524
00:21:50,790 --> 00:21:52,510
We are still far behind you.

525
00:21:52,790 --> 00:21:53,960
When you have time,

526
00:21:54,070 --> 00:21:55,030
tell us more about

527
00:21:55,030 --> 00:21:56,240
house-building.

528
00:21:56,510 --> 00:21:57,960
Although we deal in
construction materials,

529
00:21:57,960 --> 00:21:59,400
it should be closely related

530
00:21:59,400 --> 00:22:00,680
to house-building.

531
00:22:00,960 --> 00:22:02,750
It's always better to know more,

532
00:22:02,750 --> 00:22:03,150
right?

533
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:04,590
I want to listen too.

534
00:22:04,590 --> 00:22:05,550
Xiaolan,

535
00:22:05,550 --> 00:22:07,550
let me know when you start the class.

536
00:22:08,110 --> 00:22:09,880
Well, I'll charge tuition fees.

537
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:11,110
No problem.

538
00:22:11,920 --> 00:22:13,550
I'm leaving now.

539
00:22:14,050 --> 00:22:14,960
Going to check on Cheng?

540
00:22:14,960 --> 00:22:15,400
Yes.

541
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:17,040
Be safe on the road.

542
00:22:17,310 --> 00:22:18,040
Okay. Bye.

543
00:22:18,120 --> 00:22:18,650
Bye-bye.

544
00:22:23,200 --> 00:22:25,330
Why does Xiaolan look so preoccupied?

545
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:27,200
You haven't seen Cheng.

546
00:22:27,200 --> 00:22:29,460
He looks even more worried than Xiaolan.

547
00:22:32,750 --> 00:22:33,410
Zhou Cheng.

548
00:22:33,750 --> 00:22:35,550
The doctor just said that Yan...

549
00:22:37,110 --> 00:22:37,720
Auntie,

550
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:39,130
is something wrong?

551
00:22:41,680 --> 00:22:42,440
You didn't tell her

552
00:22:42,440 --> 00:22:43,440
what I said to you?

553
00:22:44,270 --> 00:22:44,830
Auntie,

554
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:45,920
I've already told you

555
00:22:45,920 --> 00:22:47,000
it's impossible.

556
00:22:47,510 --> 00:22:48,790
There's no need to tell Xiaolan.

557
00:22:48,790 --> 00:22:50,050
What's your plan then?

558
00:22:50,240 --> 00:22:51,070
My daughter got injured

559
00:22:51,070 --> 00:22:52,200
while working on a case with you, right?

560
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:53,440
You're discharged now,

561
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:54,070
but what about her?

562
00:22:54,070 --> 00:22:55,000
She's so pitiful.

563
00:22:55,000 --> 00:22:55,440
The injuries on her arms

564
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:56,970
and her back are so severe.

565
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:59,960
It hurts so much every time
they change her dressings.

566
00:22:59,960 --> 00:23:00,550
Auntie,

567
00:23:01,350 --> 00:23:02,880
may I ask what this is about?

568
00:23:03,310 --> 00:23:04,160
-Alright, since he won't tell you,
-Xiaolan.

569
00:23:04,160 --> 00:23:04,720
I will.

570
00:23:04,740 --> 00:23:06,350
This has nothing to do with you.

571
00:23:06,350 --> 00:23:07,110
Don't ask about it.

572
00:23:07,110 --> 00:23:08,680
How can it have nothing to do with her?

573
00:23:08,680 --> 00:23:10,070
What do you mean?

574
00:23:10,640 --> 00:23:11,790
I'm telling you one more time—

575
00:23:11,790 --> 00:23:13,720
my daughter got seriously injured

576
00:23:13,720 --> 00:23:14,960
while working on a case with you.

577
00:23:14,960 --> 00:23:15,720
Her future—

578
00:23:15,800 --> 00:23:16,550
her whole life—

579
00:23:16,550 --> 00:23:17,960
you have to take responsibility for it.

580
00:23:17,960 --> 00:23:19,240
Auntie, I've told you

581
00:23:19,350 --> 00:23:20,950
I will take responsibility,

582
00:23:21,110 --> 00:23:22,040
but not in the way

583
00:23:23,070 --> 00:23:23,930
you suggested.

584
00:23:41,920 --> 00:23:42,980
Xiaolan, sit down.

585
00:23:43,050 --> 00:23:43,860
Let's talk.

586
00:23:51,240 --> 00:23:52,110
You want to talk about

587
00:23:52,110 --> 00:23:53,640
Jiang Yan's mother, right?

588
00:23:54,640 --> 00:23:56,200
She wants you to marry Jiang Yan?

589
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:57,070
But I already told her

590
00:23:57,070 --> 00:23:58,200
that's impossible.

591
00:23:58,480 --> 00:24:00,070
I can help Jiang Yan find a doctor

592
00:24:00,070 --> 00:24:00,800
to treat her,

593
00:24:01,070 --> 00:24:01,830
but anything else

594
00:24:01,830 --> 00:24:03,090
is really impossible.

595
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:05,270
Besides, we've long agreed on
the boundaries

596
00:24:05,270 --> 00:24:06,790
between helping someone
and showing gratitude,

597
00:24:06,790 --> 00:24:07,240
right?

598
00:24:07,750 --> 00:24:09,010
Why are you panicking?

599
00:24:09,160 --> 00:24:10,160
I'm not mad.

600
00:24:10,830 --> 00:24:11,720
I trust you.

601
00:24:12,960 --> 00:24:14,400
But it's not surprising

602
00:24:14,400 --> 00:24:15,680
that Jiang Yan's mother said that.

603
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:17,410
After all, when she was little...

604
00:24:17,410 --> 00:24:18,000
That was

605
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:19,460
when we were really young.

606
00:24:19,550 --> 00:24:21,510
Later, her family moved to Jinling,

607
00:24:21,510 --> 00:24:22,880
and we barely saw each other
after that.

608
00:24:22,880 --> 00:24:23,920
And Jiang Yan has long

609
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:24,780
known about us.

610
00:24:24,790 --> 00:24:25,440
It's just her mother

611
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:26,970
trying to play matchmaker.

612
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:29,680
Her mother is probably just worried

613
00:24:29,680 --> 00:24:31,000
that this incident will affect

614
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:32,130
Jiang Yan's future.

615
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:34,310
After all, appearance

616
00:24:34,310 --> 00:24:35,970
is quite important for a girl.

617
00:24:38,880 --> 00:24:39,940
But no matter what,

618
00:24:40,350 --> 00:24:41,070
I will definitely

619
00:24:41,070 --> 00:24:42,270
make it clear to them.

620
00:24:42,550 --> 00:24:43,080
Xiaolan.

621
00:24:43,510 --> 00:24:44,240
Don't worry.

622
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:45,720
I trust you.

623
00:24:46,880 --> 00:24:48,140
What I'm worried about

624
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:49,310
is your safety.

625
00:24:51,440 --> 00:24:52,720
You escaped this time,

626
00:24:53,720 --> 00:24:55,320
but what if it happens again?

627
00:24:57,480 --> 00:24:58,480
But now that even Jiang Yan

628
00:24:58,480 --> 00:24:59,480
has been dragged into this,

629
00:24:59,480 --> 00:25:02,140
I absolutely cannot
give up the investigation.

630
00:25:05,640 --> 00:25:06,170
Alright.

631
00:25:06,790 --> 00:25:07,510
Let's not talk about this.

632
00:25:07,510 --> 00:25:08,200
I'm hungry.

633
00:25:08,750 --> 00:25:09,550
I'll go cook.

634
00:25:10,480 --> 00:25:11,480
Noodles with bean paste?

635
00:25:11,480 --> 00:25:11,880
Okay.

636
00:25:27,880 --> 00:25:29,440
I know you won't give up.

637
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:31,310
I'm just worried—

638
00:25:31,920 --> 00:25:33,520
are you facing these dangers

639
00:25:33,550 --> 00:25:35,350
really only because of the case,

640
00:25:36,310 --> 00:25:37,070
or could it also have something to do

641
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:38,270
with my presence?

642
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:41,600
How much longer can I stay here with you?

643
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:43,350
Should I get closer to you

644
00:25:43,350 --> 00:25:44,550
or stay away from you?

645
00:25:46,640 --> 00:25:48,040
I have so many questions,

646
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:49,680
but I can't find the answers,

647
00:25:49,680 --> 00:25:51,410
and I can't bring myself to ask.

648
00:26:02,030 --> 00:26:02,690
Auntie Liu.

649
00:26:03,030 --> 00:26:04,680
Gong Yang, what brings you here?

650
00:26:04,680 --> 00:26:06,510
I'm here to get the blueprints
from Ms. Xia.

651
00:26:06,510 --> 00:26:07,880
Xiaolan isn't back yet.

652
00:26:09,610 --> 00:26:10,070
I'm back.

653
00:26:10,070 --> 00:26:10,670
Gong Yang.

654
00:26:11,330 --> 00:26:12,200
You want the blueprints, right?

655
00:26:12,200 --> 00:26:13,200
I totally forgot.

656
00:26:13,480 --> 00:26:14,840
You didn't come to the office
this afternoon.

657
00:26:14,840 --> 00:26:15,830
I just got off work,

658
00:26:15,830 --> 00:26:17,110
so I stopped by on my way.

659
00:26:17,110 --> 00:26:18,030
Mr. Mao said we must
have the blueprints ready

660
00:26:18,030 --> 00:26:19,030
at work tomorrow.

661
00:26:19,270 --> 00:26:19,550
Wait,

662
00:26:19,550 --> 00:26:20,810
why didn't you call me?

663
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:22,740
I did, but I couldn't get through.

664
00:26:25,790 --> 00:26:26,790
The battery died.

665
00:26:26,970 --> 00:26:27,570
I'm sorry.

666
00:26:27,590 --> 00:26:28,400
I was just too busy this afternoon.

667
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:28,880
Wait a moment here.

668
00:26:28,880 --> 00:26:29,640
I'll go upstairs and get them for you.

669
00:26:29,640 --> 00:26:30,030
Okay.

670
00:26:33,550 --> 00:26:35,680
She's been so scatterbrained lately.

671
00:26:35,720 --> 00:26:37,050
Ms. Xia is just too busy.

672
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:40,640
Sorry for making you
come all this way today.

673
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:42,240
I'll count this as overtime.

674
00:26:42,790 --> 00:26:44,520
Mr. Mao said he missed you a bit.

675
00:26:45,130 --> 00:26:45,780
I know.

676
00:26:45,880 --> 00:26:47,680
He just wants to scold me, right?

677
00:26:48,470 --> 00:26:49,350
We can still handle it.

678
00:26:49,350 --> 00:26:50,950
Ms. Xia, get some rest early.

679
00:26:53,400 --> 00:26:54,410
Get home safely.

680
00:26:54,550 --> 00:26:55,880
Sure thing, Ms. Xia. See you tomorrow.

681
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:56,880
See you tomorrow.

682
00:27:20,110 --> 00:27:21,640
If things keep going like this,

683
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:23,500
everything will fall into chaos,

684
00:27:24,070 --> 00:27:26,130
and they'll notice something's off.

685
00:27:27,030 --> 00:27:27,640
Xiaolan.

686
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:29,390
Come have some chicken soup.

687
00:27:31,240 --> 00:27:31,700
Come on.

688
00:27:32,030 --> 00:27:33,430
Drink it while it's warm.

689
00:27:33,510 --> 00:27:34,270
Thanks, Mom.

690
00:27:36,270 --> 00:27:37,510
There's been so much going on lately.

691
00:27:37,510 --> 00:27:38,960
It's been tough, hasn't it?

692
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:40,920
If you're tired, just have some rest.

693
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:42,520
But I don't have time to rest.

694
00:27:44,550 --> 00:27:45,270
However, it's really about time

695
00:27:45,270 --> 00:27:46,440
I hire an assistant.

696
00:27:47,550 --> 00:27:48,000
Mom.

697
00:27:48,110 --> 00:27:50,170
How's You Li been performing lately?

698
00:27:50,310 --> 00:27:51,070
You Li?

699
00:27:52,980 --> 00:27:54,710
That girl is really quite good.

700
00:27:54,790 --> 00:27:56,830
She's hardworking and willing to learn.

701
00:27:56,830 --> 00:27:57,270
You know,

702
00:27:57,270 --> 00:27:58,350
she's been really fluent

703
00:27:58,350 --> 00:27:59,410
in English lately.

704
00:27:59,550 --> 00:28:00,640
She has no problem

705
00:28:00,640 --> 00:28:02,640
communicating with clients at all.

706
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:04,720
Do you want her to be your assistant?

707
00:28:06,110 --> 00:28:07,370
I think that will work.

708
00:28:14,310 --> 00:28:14,830
You Li.

709
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:16,930
Come here when you're done.

710
00:28:24,640 --> 00:28:25,310
Ms. Xia.

711
00:28:25,510 --> 00:28:26,370
Come, sit down.

712
00:28:29,550 --> 00:28:30,070
You Li,

713
00:28:30,480 --> 00:28:31,960
you've been with us
since the store opened.

714
00:28:31,960 --> 00:28:33,490
You're a veteran employee,

715
00:28:33,750 --> 00:28:35,640
and you've been performing very well.

716
00:28:35,640 --> 00:28:36,720
During training before,

717
00:28:36,720 --> 00:28:37,750
I told you all

718
00:28:38,240 --> 00:28:39,590
that as long as you perform well,

719
00:28:39,590 --> 00:28:41,850
there will be better job opportunities.

720
00:28:42,030 --> 00:28:42,920
So I wanted to

721
00:28:42,920 --> 00:28:44,200
ask for your opinion:

722
00:28:44,590 --> 00:28:46,790
would you be willing to be my assistant?

723
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:49,830
So here's the thing.

724
00:28:49,830 --> 00:28:51,070
I'm about to start

725
00:28:51,100 --> 00:28:52,200
a real estate company—

726
00:28:52,200 --> 00:28:53,680
buying land and building houses.

727
00:28:53,680 --> 00:28:55,000
The design work

728
00:28:55,030 --> 00:28:55,920
of my uncle's projects

729
00:28:55,920 --> 00:28:56,550
will also be merged

730
00:28:56,550 --> 00:28:57,440
into my studio.

731
00:28:57,510 --> 00:28:58,570
So as my assistant,

732
00:28:58,680 --> 00:29:00,650
you'll need to not only
handle matters for Luna,

733
00:29:00,650 --> 00:29:01,970
but also take care of

734
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:03,590
the real estate and design work.

735
00:29:03,590 --> 00:29:04,190
Oh, right—

736
00:29:04,250 --> 00:29:05,240
there's also a materials center.

737
00:29:05,240 --> 00:29:06,030
But there isn't much work

738
00:29:06,030 --> 00:29:06,720
over there.

739
00:29:06,720 --> 00:29:08,720
You just need to go there occasionally.

740
00:29:08,720 --> 00:29:09,480
Ms. Xia,

741
00:29:10,110 --> 00:29:11,240
with so much work,

742
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:13,320
I'm afraid I can't handle it.

743
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:15,200
Yeah,

744
00:29:15,510 --> 00:29:16,790
I know it's not easy.

745
00:29:17,350 --> 00:29:19,580
I could put an ad in the paper
for a college student,

746
00:29:19,580 --> 00:29:20,540
but I think

747
00:29:20,770 --> 00:29:21,280
your ability

748
00:29:21,280 --> 00:29:22,590
is no worse than theirs,

749
00:29:22,590 --> 00:29:23,960
and you have more

750
00:29:23,960 --> 00:29:25,620
work experience than they do.

751
00:29:27,240 --> 00:29:28,070
How about this?

752
00:29:28,070 --> 00:29:29,480
You don't have to give me an answer
right away.

753
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:30,940
Go back and think about it.

754
00:29:31,070 --> 00:29:32,240
As for the salary,

755
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:33,600
-I think...
-Ms. Xia.

756
00:29:34,310 --> 00:29:36,110
Thank you for your recognition.

757
00:29:36,480 --> 00:29:37,480
But I'm afraid

758
00:29:37,550 --> 00:29:39,350
I still can't be your assistant.

759
00:29:39,590 --> 00:29:40,650
I'm sorry, Ms. Xia.

760
00:29:40,720 --> 00:29:42,180
I'm going back to work now.

761
00:29:42,310 --> 00:29:42,920
Thank you.

762
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:51,720
You Li?

763
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:54,530
She's quite motivated,

764
00:29:54,590 --> 00:29:55,720
and she loves to learn.

765
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:56,350
Why would she turn down

766
00:29:56,350 --> 00:29:57,640
such a good opportunity?

767
00:29:57,640 --> 00:29:58,270
Exactly.

768
00:29:58,440 --> 00:30:00,030
At first,

769
00:30:00,030 --> 00:30:01,510
she seemed quite interested.

770
00:30:01,510 --> 00:30:03,040
But later, I don't know why,

771
00:30:03,400 --> 00:30:04,350
without even considering it,

772
00:30:04,350 --> 00:30:05,070
she just stood up,

773
00:30:05,070 --> 00:30:06,000
bowed and left.

774
00:30:06,880 --> 00:30:08,510
Could it be that the workload's so heavy

775
00:30:08,510 --> 00:30:09,590
that she got scared away?

776
00:30:09,590 --> 00:30:11,030
The workload is indeed heavy,

777
00:30:11,030 --> 00:30:12,430
but I couldn't lie to her.

778
00:30:12,800 --> 00:30:14,210
But I also told her

779
00:30:14,240 --> 00:30:15,000
it's mainly about

780
00:30:15,000 --> 00:30:16,260
the work at the studio.

781
00:30:16,350 --> 00:30:17,270
There won't be much work

782
00:30:17,270 --> 00:30:19,130
at Happy Life Materials and Luna.

783
00:30:20,800 --> 00:30:23,200
Whoever started the trouble should end it.

784
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:24,440
I'd better step in

785
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:25,940
to handle this matter.

786
00:30:26,310 --> 00:30:27,030
Why?

787
00:30:27,510 --> 00:30:28,590
What does it have to do with you?

788
00:30:28,590 --> 00:30:29,440
I guess

789
00:30:29,550 --> 00:30:30,720
You Li

790
00:30:30,720 --> 00:30:31,550
is just self-conscious.

791
00:30:31,550 --> 00:30:32,720
It must be because of that incident

792
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:34,980
that she feels too embarrassed to see me.

793
00:30:36,070 --> 00:30:36,680
Wei.

794
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:37,720
That incident

795
00:30:37,720 --> 00:30:39,070
happened ages ago.

796
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:40,480
I'm afraid little You Li

797
00:30:40,480 --> 00:30:42,410
doesn't even remember who you are.

798
00:30:43,350 --> 00:30:44,750
I think Zhenzhu is right.

799
00:30:45,550 --> 00:30:47,550
You Li probably has other concerns.

800
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:48,830
What concerns?

801
00:30:48,830 --> 00:30:49,640
She's just a young girl.

802
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:50,750
What concerns could she possibly have?

803
00:30:50,750 --> 00:30:52,750
I'm the only possible concern here.

804
00:30:52,750 --> 00:30:53,680
Yeah, right. You're her concern.

805
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:54,340
Yes, right.

806
00:30:54,440 --> 00:30:55,310
Leave this to me.

807
00:30:55,310 --> 00:30:56,270
You definitely are.

808
00:30:56,270 --> 00:30:56,790
San!

809
00:30:57,240 --> 00:30:58,310
We'd like to order more.

810
00:30:58,310 --> 00:30:58,840
Alright.

811
00:30:59,590 --> 00:31:00,920
Sis Bai, this one dish isn't enough.

812
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:01,680
Think about it. What other dishes
do you want?

813
00:31:01,680 --> 00:31:02,480
What other dishes do you want?

814
00:31:02,480 --> 00:31:03,410
Look at the menu.

815
00:31:04,350 --> 00:31:05,640
That matter you asked me to check
last time—

816
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:07,030
I've asked a friend
who does business in Nanyang

817
00:31:07,030 --> 00:31:07,760
look into it.

818
00:31:08,070 --> 00:31:09,010
How about shredded potatoes?

819
00:31:09,010 --> 00:31:10,110
Let's have shredded potatoes then.

820
00:31:10,110 --> 00:31:10,550
Sure.

821
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:12,400
Thanks, San.

822
00:31:12,480 --> 00:31:13,140
No problem.

823
00:31:35,720 --> 00:31:36,780
Don't you feel hot?

824
00:31:37,350 --> 00:31:38,810
I'm used to the heat by now.

825
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:40,850
Still investigating that worker?

826
00:31:43,150 --> 00:31:45,010
We've got news about that worker.

827
00:31:45,240 --> 00:31:45,970
We found him,

828
00:31:46,440 --> 00:31:47,700
but he died in Nanyang.

829
00:31:48,270 --> 00:31:49,730
I suspect he was murdered.

830
00:31:51,000 --> 00:31:51,880
This matter

831
00:31:52,110 --> 00:31:54,240
is getting more and more complicated.

832
00:31:55,200 --> 00:31:56,000
Will Jiang Yan

833
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:57,780
still be involved in the case
going forward?

834
00:31:57,780 --> 00:31:59,030
You know Jiang Yan.

835
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:00,440
After what happened,

836
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:02,370
she'll definitely see it through.

837
00:32:02,380 --> 00:32:03,240
She also wants to see

838
00:32:03,240 --> 00:32:04,640
who's so bold as to

839
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:06,590
target even lawyers

840
00:32:06,590 --> 00:32:07,590
and prosecutors.

841
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:09,680
According to police leads,

842
00:32:10,110 --> 00:32:10,680
it's likely related

843
00:32:10,680 --> 00:32:11,810
to a smuggling ring.

844
00:32:12,920 --> 00:32:15,250
So Jiang Yan will definitely be involved.

845
00:32:16,480 --> 00:32:17,110
Cheng,

846
00:32:17,590 --> 00:32:18,550
aren't you worried

847
00:32:18,550 --> 00:32:19,810
Xiaolan will be upset?

848
00:32:22,240 --> 00:32:23,160
Xiaolan won't get upset

849
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:24,620
over something like this.

850
00:32:25,110 --> 00:32:25,920
However...

851
00:32:26,480 --> 00:32:27,110
Look.

852
00:32:27,480 --> 00:32:27,960
Look.

853
00:32:28,270 --> 00:32:29,000
I knew it.

854
00:32:29,030 --> 00:32:30,310
It surely wasn't because

855
00:32:30,310 --> 00:32:31,110
you and Xiaolan were busy with work

856
00:32:31,110 --> 00:32:32,430
that you two didn't get married.

857
00:32:32,430 --> 00:32:33,760
Xiaolan is indeed busy,

858
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:35,590
but I do have

859
00:32:36,210 --> 00:32:37,640
other concerns as well.

860
00:32:38,750 --> 00:32:41,210
You're worried this matter
will affect her?

861
00:32:43,310 --> 00:32:44,030
Look at you.

862
00:32:44,510 --> 00:32:46,270
What's wrong with you, Cheng?

863
00:32:46,730 --> 00:32:48,660
You're worrying about the future.

864
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:49,650
You know what this is called?

865
00:32:49,650 --> 00:32:50,680
Borrowing trouble.

866
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:52,000
Worrying for nothing.

867
00:32:52,350 --> 00:32:53,950
Why should you worry about Xiaolan?

868
00:32:53,950 --> 00:32:55,040
She's so smart.

869
00:32:55,070 --> 00:32:55,880
Even if problems come up in the future,

870
00:32:55,880 --> 00:32:57,610
you two can face them together.

871
00:32:57,680 --> 00:32:58,310
Look at you.

872
00:32:58,310 --> 00:32:59,480
You're usually smart.

873
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:01,010
Why are you being silly now?

874
00:33:01,010 --> 00:33:02,350
I think you traded your IQ

875
00:33:02,350 --> 00:33:03,400
for love.

876
00:33:06,070 --> 00:33:07,200
Maybe you're right.

877
00:33:08,640 --> 00:33:10,040
But when you like someone

878
00:33:10,440 --> 00:33:11,570
and care about them,

879
00:33:11,830 --> 00:33:13,030
this is only natural.

880
00:33:13,550 --> 00:33:14,310
Once you have someone to care about,

881
00:33:14,310 --> 00:33:15,440
you'll understand.

882
00:33:16,030 --> 00:33:16,640
Forget it.

883
00:33:16,960 --> 00:33:17,830
It's too much trouble.

884
00:33:17,830 --> 00:33:18,960
I don't want to know.

885
00:33:19,110 --> 00:33:20,570
I'm going to take a shower.

886
00:33:36,110 --> 00:33:36,640
I'm here.

887
00:33:37,510 --> 00:33:39,240
Here's the hamburger I bought.

888
00:33:39,880 --> 00:33:40,590
In here.

889
00:33:41,350 --> 00:33:42,010
Here you go.

890
00:33:42,710 --> 00:33:44,120
This place opened last year.

891
00:33:44,120 --> 00:33:46,350
I've wanted to come,
but never had the time.

892
00:33:46,350 --> 00:33:47,830
I didn't expect there to be
so many people inside.

893
00:33:47,830 --> 00:33:49,030
T-There were no seats left.

894
00:33:49,030 --> 00:33:50,690
Sorry to make you eat outside.

895
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:52,110
It's okay.

896
00:33:52,590 --> 00:33:53,790
It's quite nice here.

897
00:33:53,790 --> 00:33:55,050
The breeze feels nice.

898
00:33:57,320 --> 00:33:58,710
Come on, eat. It's tasty.

899
00:33:58,710 --> 00:33:59,150
Try it.

900
00:34:05,030 --> 00:34:05,640
How is it?

901
00:34:07,790 --> 00:34:09,670
It tastes a bit strange,

902
00:34:10,440 --> 00:34:12,170
but it's actually pretty good.

903
00:34:12,510 --> 00:34:14,969
It's different from
the food we usually eat.

904
00:34:16,550 --> 00:34:17,920
Well, our food is still better.

905
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:19,510
How about we go to my friend's restaurant

906
00:34:19,510 --> 00:34:20,880
and order some stir-fried dishes?

907
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:21,530
No need, really.

908
00:34:21,530 --> 00:34:22,380
This is fine.

909
00:34:23,630 --> 00:34:24,070
Okay.

910
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:30,630
Mr. Kang.

911
00:34:32,110 --> 00:34:32,960
Actually,

912
00:34:33,400 --> 00:34:35,929
I should have apologized to you
a long time ago.

913
00:34:35,929 --> 00:34:37,000
Back at the hospital,

914
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:38,280
I was too hasty.

915
00:34:40,639 --> 00:34:41,639
A-Actually,

916
00:34:41,670 --> 00:34:43,550
I've also wanted to ask you—

917
00:34:44,030 --> 00:34:44,840
what exactly happened

918
00:34:44,840 --> 00:34:45,840
back then?

919
00:34:47,030 --> 00:34:47,440
I...

920
00:34:49,710 --> 00:34:50,760
They all say...

921
00:34:51,190 --> 00:34:52,670
T-That you only liked me

922
00:34:52,670 --> 00:34:53,800
because you misjudged me,

923
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:55,860
and once you realized, you dumped me.

924
00:34:56,670 --> 00:34:57,930
Don't choke. Careful.

925
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:04,880
Actually,

926
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:08,330
it was because
my mom was sick at that time,

927
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:10,260
and I really needed money.

928
00:35:11,280 --> 00:35:12,280
Freshly steamed.

929
00:35:12,800 --> 00:35:13,400
Want some?

930
00:35:14,030 --> 00:35:14,670
Ma'am,

931
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:16,360
how much for one?

932
00:35:16,550 --> 00:35:17,080
One dime.

933
00:35:19,630 --> 00:35:20,320
Want some?

934
00:35:25,630 --> 00:35:26,630
No thanks, Ma'am.

935
00:35:26,670 --> 00:35:27,400
I'm good.

936
00:35:28,710 --> 00:35:29,300
Thank you.

937
00:35:29,300 --> 00:35:29,830
Alright.

938
00:35:42,460 --> 00:35:43,000
Auntie?

939
00:35:43,110 --> 00:35:43,730
Uncle?

940
00:35:44,280 --> 00:35:45,210
Why are you here?

941
00:35:45,550 --> 00:35:46,360
Something this serious has happened.

942
00:35:46,360 --> 00:35:47,550
How could we not come?

943
00:35:47,550 --> 00:35:49,070
Luckily, we caught the last flight.

944
00:35:49,070 --> 00:35:49,590
Yeah.

945
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:51,090
How's Wei doing, Cheng?

946
00:35:51,630 --> 00:35:52,610
I'm not sure either.

947
00:35:52,610 --> 00:35:53,670
Let's talk inside.

948
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:55,460
Look at you.

949
00:35:56,710 --> 00:35:57,570
Let me tell you.

950
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:59,130
This is Shengcheng.

951
00:36:00,440 --> 00:36:02,170
Since you did something wrong,

952
00:36:02,550 --> 00:36:04,410
you have to take responsibility!

953
00:36:05,230 --> 00:36:06,150
I could tell

954
00:36:06,550 --> 00:36:07,360
that your family

955
00:36:07,360 --> 00:36:08,490
was quite well-off,

956
00:36:09,170 --> 00:36:11,360
because you didn't even take
Gangdao merchants seriously.

957
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:12,110
So I tried

958
00:36:13,400 --> 00:36:14,460
to get close to you,

959
00:36:15,230 --> 00:36:17,550
thinking if you and your mom liked me,

960
00:36:19,320 --> 00:36:21,050
perhaps I could get some money.

961
00:36:24,470 --> 00:36:25,020
Mr. Kang.

962
00:36:25,400 --> 00:36:26,400
I'm really sorry.

963
00:36:26,480 --> 00:36:27,680
It's okay. No need...

964
00:36:28,160 --> 00:36:28,840
-It's okay. It's okay.
-I… I...

965
00:36:28,840 --> 00:36:29,440
It's okay.

966
00:36:29,590 --> 00:36:30,670
There are so many people here.

967
00:36:30,670 --> 00:36:31,320
Come on, sit.

968
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:32,070
Come on.

969
00:36:32,230 --> 00:36:33,150
Really, it's okay.

970
00:36:33,150 --> 00:36:33,750
It's okay.

971
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:34,880
Well...

972
00:36:35,960 --> 00:36:37,090
What happened then?

973
00:36:37,190 --> 00:36:39,000
Y-You were scared off by Sis Bai?

974
00:36:41,190 --> 00:36:41,840
Kind of.

975
00:36:43,070 --> 00:36:43,960
And

976
00:36:44,400 --> 00:36:46,150
I had felt terrible about it all along.

977
00:36:46,150 --> 00:36:47,290
I knew it was wrong.

978
00:36:47,960 --> 00:36:49,110
I did need money,

979
00:36:49,650 --> 00:36:51,380
but my mom had always taught me

980
00:36:51,510 --> 00:36:52,630
to be upright

981
00:36:52,630 --> 00:36:54,090
and make an honest living.

982
00:36:54,620 --> 00:36:55,350
Later,

983
00:36:55,440 --> 00:36:57,190
I saw a job ad for Luna.

984
00:36:57,920 --> 00:36:59,650
It said no degree was required,

985
00:36:59,920 --> 00:37:02,150
as long as you're hardworking and capable.

986
00:37:02,150 --> 00:37:03,110
So I gave it a try.

987
00:37:04,110 --> 00:37:04,560
See?

988
00:37:04,590 --> 00:37:05,710
Isn't that great?

989
00:37:06,110 --> 00:37:07,360
Since we've talked

990
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:08,290
everything out,

991
00:37:08,630 --> 00:37:10,030
don't feel burdened.

992
00:37:10,240 --> 00:37:11,450
And don't let this

993
00:37:11,480 --> 00:37:12,880
stop you from working for Xiaolan.

994
00:37:12,880 --> 00:37:14,320
It's such a good opportunity.

995
00:37:14,320 --> 00:37:15,030
From now on, we can also

996
00:37:15,030 --> 00:37:17,160
meet openly and without awkwardness.

997
00:37:17,230 --> 00:37:17,960
Mr. Kang.

998
00:37:19,230 --> 00:37:20,560
You've misunderstood.

999
00:37:20,630 --> 00:37:22,550
It wasn't because of that.

1000
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:25,110
Then what is it?

1001
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:26,710
Working for Xiaolan

1002
00:37:26,710 --> 00:37:27,670
is a great opportunity.

1003
00:37:27,670 --> 00:37:28,840
Don't be silly.

1004
00:37:30,030 --> 00:37:30,480
I...

1005
00:37:31,710 --> 00:37:33,630
I-I can't be Ms. Xia's assistant.

1006
00:37:43,640 --> 00:37:44,510
Just pull over here.

1007
00:37:44,510 --> 00:37:46,710
The road ahead is too narrow for the car.

1008
00:37:51,150 --> 00:37:52,410
Well, be careful then.

1009
00:37:56,590 --> 00:37:57,110
You.

1010
00:37:58,030 --> 00:38:00,000
About Xiaolan's offer

1011
00:38:00,000 --> 00:38:01,530
for you to be her assistant,

1012
00:38:01,550 --> 00:38:02,750
give it more thought.

1013
00:38:03,240 --> 00:38:04,080
I think it's a

1014
00:38:04,110 --> 00:38:05,570
really good opportunity.

1015
00:38:06,070 --> 00:38:07,710
And the fact that Xiaolan wants you

1016
00:38:07,710 --> 00:38:09,670
proves she thinks you're capable enough.

1017
00:38:09,670 --> 00:38:11,400
You can be a bit more confident.

1018
00:38:19,260 --> 00:38:20,390
Let me help you down.

1019
00:38:26,110 --> 00:38:27,400
Here. Careful.

1020
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:30,400
Thank you.

1021
00:38:30,510 --> 00:38:31,150
No problem.

1022
00:38:31,150 --> 00:38:31,960
Be careful.

1023
00:38:32,190 --> 00:38:32,630
Okay.

1024
00:38:32,750 --> 00:38:33,660
I'll go in now.

1025
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:12,200
She seems like she wants to do it.

1026
00:39:13,000 --> 00:39:14,530
Why does she keep refusing?

1027
00:39:20,710 --> 00:39:21,190
Mom.

1028
00:39:21,760 --> 00:39:22,590
I'm back.

1029
00:39:25,550 --> 00:39:26,070
Dad?

1030
00:39:26,930 --> 00:39:28,190
You... You're home?

1031
00:39:29,070 --> 00:39:31,270
I thought you had the night shift today.

1032
00:39:32,960 --> 00:39:34,560
You've been drinking again.

1033
00:39:39,070 --> 00:39:40,480
So what if I drank?

1034
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:42,400
You little bitch.

1035
00:39:43,920 --> 00:39:45,980
You really are my good daughter, huh?

1036
00:39:46,700 --> 00:39:48,100
Think you're all grown up

1037
00:39:48,590 --> 00:39:49,990
and want to run away, huh?

1038
00:39:51,880 --> 00:39:53,550
I knew something was

1039
00:39:53,550 --> 00:39:54,590
off lately.

1040
00:39:55,110 --> 00:39:57,020
You thought you could hide this from me?

1041
00:39:57,020 --> 00:39:58,940
Your mother told me everything!

1042
00:39:59,230 --> 00:40:00,290
Trying to run away?

1043
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:01,360
No...

1044
00:40:02,250 --> 00:40:04,000
You want to go off on your own
and live the good life?

1045
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:04,590
No...

1046
00:40:04,840 --> 00:40:06,100
I'll beat you to death!

1047
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:07,190
You!

1048
00:40:07,440 --> 00:40:09,960
I'll kill you and your mother,

1049
00:40:10,110 --> 00:40:12,230
so you give up on that idea!

1050
00:40:13,070 --> 00:40:13,800
Get in there!

1051
00:40:17,030 --> 00:40:17,590
Mom!

1052
00:40:18,280 --> 00:40:18,840
Mom!

1053
00:40:19,030 --> 00:40:20,590
Mom, what's wrong? Mom!

1054
00:40:21,090 --> 00:40:22,250
Run... Run...

1055
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:23,000
Scream!

1056
00:40:23,510 --> 00:40:24,960
Scream louder!

1057
00:40:25,320 --> 00:40:26,960
Call all the neighbors over

1058
00:40:27,280 --> 00:40:29,170
and let them see your mother naked!

1059
00:40:29,170 --> 00:40:30,820
Mom! Don't! Mom!

1060
00:40:31,670 --> 00:40:32,510
Don't! Mom!

1061
00:40:32,920 --> 00:40:33,630
Don't! Mom!

1062
00:40:33,630 --> 00:40:34,960
That sounds like You Li.

1063
00:40:35,400 --> 00:40:36,030
Bastard!

1064
00:40:36,190 --> 00:40:37,650
It really sounds like her.

1065
00:40:37,880 --> 00:40:38,550
She's my mother!

1066
00:40:38,550 --> 00:40:39,920
She's also your wife!

1067
00:40:40,030 --> 00:40:40,630
You beast!

1068
00:40:40,710 --> 00:40:41,710
I'm a beast?

1069
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:43,280
Then what are you?

1070
00:40:43,590 --> 00:40:44,940
You're not my own flesh and blood.

1071
00:40:44,940 --> 00:40:46,950
No matter how I raise you, it's useless!

1072
00:40:46,950 --> 00:40:49,010
I'd be better off raising a dog!

1073
00:40:49,400 --> 00:40:50,150
I'll

1074
00:40:50,510 --> 00:40:52,230
break your legs right now!

1075
00:40:55,320 --> 00:40:57,710
I'm going to tell the police right now!

1076
00:40:57,920 --> 00:40:59,480
I'm going to tell the subdistrict office!

1077
00:40:59,480 --> 00:40:59,880
You...

1078
00:41:02,030 --> 00:41:02,840
Run then!

1079
00:41:03,280 --> 00:41:05,210
Run and I'll beat your mom to death!

1080
00:41:07,880 --> 00:41:08,940
What are you doing?

1081
00:41:09,630 --> 00:41:10,480
Let go!

1082
00:41:12,970 --> 00:41:13,960
What are you doing?

1083
00:41:13,960 --> 00:41:15,480
I'll fight you to the death!

1084
00:41:15,480 --> 00:41:17,280
I'll fight you to the death! I...

1085
00:41:19,880 --> 00:41:21,410
I'll fight you to the death!

1086
00:41:24,400 --> 00:41:26,320
Come any closer and I'll kill you!

1087
00:41:26,670 --> 00:41:27,510
Kill me?

1088
00:41:28,230 --> 00:41:30,090
Do you even know how to use a knife?

1089
00:41:31,030 --> 00:41:31,960
I'll kill you!

1090
00:41:34,150 --> 00:41:35,150
Kill me then!

1091
00:42:03,070 --> 00:42:03,650
What happened?

1092
00:42:03,650 --> 00:42:04,780
Did a thief break in?

1093
00:42:04,840 --> 00:42:05,710
I'm here. Don't be afraid.

1094
00:42:05,710 --> 00:42:07,040
What happened? Tell me!

1095
00:42:07,510 --> 00:42:08,030
He...

1096
00:42:08,320 --> 00:42:09,760
He killed my mom.

1097
00:42:10,070 --> 00:42:10,730
Your mom...

1098
00:42:19,150 --> 00:42:19,590
You Li!

1099
00:42:19,920 --> 00:42:21,110
Your mom's still alive.

1100
00:42:21,110 --> 00:42:21,880
Mom!

1101
00:42:23,190 --> 00:42:23,800
Mom!

1102
00:42:24,880 --> 00:42:25,400
Mom.

1103
00:42:26,190 --> 00:42:26,840
Kang Wei.

1104
00:42:27,280 --> 00:42:28,000
Save my mom.

1105
00:42:28,280 --> 00:42:29,110
I'm begging you!

1106
00:42:29,110 --> 00:42:30,840
I'll do anything to repay you!

1107
00:42:31,670 --> 00:42:32,320
You Li.

1108
00:42:32,510 --> 00:42:33,840
Stop talking nonsense.

1109
00:42:33,840 --> 00:42:34,880
Get your mom and that guy

1110
00:42:34,880 --> 00:42:35,730
into my car.

1111
00:42:35,760 --> 00:42:37,490
I'll take them to the hospital.

1112
00:42:37,960 --> 00:42:39,550
Why save that beast?

1113
00:42:40,110 --> 00:42:41,000
Don't be stupid.

1114
00:42:41,000 --> 00:42:42,600
Leaving him to die is murder!

1115
00:42:42,610 --> 00:42:43,190
What could be

1116
00:42:43,190 --> 00:42:44,150
more important than yourself?
